OL,3,CPolicing Board urged to probe
OL,4,Callegations of police surveillance of
OL,5,Cjournalists
OL,7,FThe Policing Board has been asked to
OL,8,Fset up an inquiry into allegations
OL,9,Fthat journalists in Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fwere subject to unlawful covert
OL,11,Fsurveillance by police.
OL,13,FAmnesty International and the
OL,14,FCommittee on the Administration of
OL,15,FJustice (CAJ) have written to the
OL,16,Fboard, the oversight body for the
OL,17,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,18,F(PSNI), raising "serious concerns over
OL,19,Fhow widespread the practice of
OL,20,Fsurveillance of journalists and others
OL,21,Fmay have been".
