OL,3,CPolicing Board urged to probe
OL,4,Callegations of police surveillance of
OL,5,Cjournalists
OL,7,FIt comes after a tribunal was told
OL,8,Fthat police mounted a covert
OL,9,Fsurveillance operation following the
OL,10,Farrest of two journalists in a bid to
OL,11,Funmask one of their sources.
OL,13,FThe Investigatory Powers Tribunal
OL,14,F(IPT) was told last week that the
OL,15,Farrest of film makers Barry McCaffrey
OL,16,Fand Trevor Birney in 2018 was a
OL,17,F"disruptive" tactic to see if the
OL,18,Freporters would reach out to the
OL,19,Fsource after their release from
OL,20,Fcustody.
