OL,7,FThe tribunal is examining allegations
OL,8,Fthat the award-winning journalists
OL,9,Fwere subject to unlawful covert
OL,10,Fsurveillance by UK authorities.
OL,12,FIn 2018, Northern Ireland-based Mr
OL,13,FMcCaffrey and Mr Birney were
OL,14,Fcontroversially arrested as part of a
OL,15,Fpolice investigation into the alleged
OL,16,Fleaking of a confidential document
OL,17,Fthat appeared in a documentary they
OL,18,Fmade on a Troubles massacre.
