OL,7,FThe following year, the two
OL,8,Fjournalists lodged a complaint with
OL,9,Fthe IPT asking it to establish whether
OL,10,Fthere had been any unlawful
OL,11,Fsurveillance of them.
OL,13,FThe letter to Policing Board
OL,14,Fchairwoman Deirdre Toner, has been
OL,15,Fsent by Patrick Corrigan from Amnesty
OL,16,Fand Daniel Holder from the CAJ.
