OL,3,CPolicing Board urged to probe
OL,4,Callegations of police surveillance of
OL,5,Cjournalists
OL,7,FIt states: "Our organisations continue
OL,8,Fto share serious concerns about how
OL,9,Fwidespread the practice of the use of
OL,10,Fcovert surveillance powers against
OL,11,Fjournalists and others may have been.
OL,13,F"As you will appreciate, the IPT will
OL,14,Fbe limited to the particular
OL,15,Fcircumstances of the specific case
OL,16,Fbefore it, rather than the question of
OL,17,Fwider PSNI practices in this area.
