OL,3,CPolicing Board urged to probe
OL,4,Callegations of police surveillance of
OL,5,Cjournalists
OL,7,F"Despite these limitations, this case
OL,8,Fhas already revealed that such
OL,9,Fsurveillance and has been deployed
OL,10,Fagainst multiple journalists on
OL,11,Fmultiple occasions under multiple
OL,12,Fchief constables ` a pattern of
OL,13,Fpotential unlawful activity and breach
OL,14,Fof the European Convention of Human
OL,15,FRights.
OL,17,F"Given this, we are writing to again
OL,18,Fpress for action from the Policing
OL,19,FBoard."
