OL,7,FThey continued: "We repeat our request
OL,8,Fto the board to conduct an inquiry,
OL,9,Funder the powers vested in you under
OL,10,Fthe Police (Northern Ireland) Act
OL,11,F2000, into PSNI use of surveillance
OL,12,Fpowers against journalists, lawyers
OL,13,Fand other human rights defenders.
