OL,7,F"Failing that, we wish to enquire how
OL,8,Fthe board plans to fulfil its role
OL,9,Feffectively ensuring PSNI human rights
OL,10,Fcompliance with respect to this matter
OL,11,Fwhich not only has the potential to
OL,12,Fundermine public confidence in
OL,13,Fpolicing but also in policing
OL,14,Foversight mechanisms."
OL,16,FA Policing Board spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"The Policing Board will consider the
OL,18,Fcorrespondence received from Amnesty
OL,19,Fat its monthly meeting on Thursday."
